skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie year trivia
des: In this skill, user can take part in a trivia about the year in which a movie was released. Alexa will ask 5 questions with multiple choices as possible answer and user needs to respond with the option number that is the answer. The result is summarised at the end of the trivia.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
